Revision history for Perl extension Games::NES::ROM

0.08 2013-11-28
 - Avoid warnings when reading INES files
 - Use Module::Runtime for loading modules (RT #91015)

0.07 2010-07-28
 - add README to dist

0.06 2010-07-28
 - factored out iNES loading and added UNIF loading
 - added the ROM database from Nestopia
 - moosified all classes

0.05 2007-08-01
 - error handling on file open
 - switch to module::install

0.04 2007-02-26
 - repackaged -- no functional changes

0.03 2006-08-03
 - more tests

0.02 2006-08-02
 - store raw chunks for CHR and PRG banks
 - added sprite() method

0.01 2006-08-01
 - original version
